Package: neuromosaic
Title: Rich Reports and Interactive Exploration for Neuroimaging Clusters
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", , "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1108-4866"))
Description: Generates publication-ready PDF/HTML reports from
    neuroimaging statistical maps. Thresholds stat maps, finds clusters,
    annotates peaks with MNI coordinates and atlas labels, extracts
    design-aware time courses, and renders formatted tables and
    formula-driven plots. Also provides an interactive Shiny explorer as
    an optional UI layer. The computation engine has zero Shiny
    dependencies and can be used programmatically.
